kaḥ punar anayor vyatireke doṣaḥ, yenaite yatnena rakṣaṇīye kathite ity āha. rogopahatasāmarthyo yathā puruṣaḥ sarvakarmasu gamanabhojanādiṣv akarmaṇyo bhavati, tathā smṛtisaṃprajanyābhyāṃ vikalaṃ cittaṃ sarvakarmasu dhyānādhyayanādilakṣaṇeṣu.

<commentary>anayoḥ samudāyābhāve doṣam uktvā pratyekam abhāve kathayitum āha.

na vidyate saṃprajanyaṃ yasmiṃs tad asaṃprajanyam. taccittaṃ yasya tasya. śrutacintābhāvanāmayaprajñāpariniṣṭhitaṃ vastu na smaraṇam adhivasati. tanmūlaṃ ca sarvaṃ kalyāṇam. kim iva? yathā sacchidrakumbhe mukhanikśiptam udakam adhastād gacchati nāvatiṣṭhate.</commentary>

idam aparaṃ tadvayatireke dūṣaṇam āha. bahavo 'pi bahuśrutāḥ tathā śraddhāvanto yatnaparāḥ śikṣāyām ādarakāriṇaḥ asaṃprajanyadoṣeṇa āpattikaluṣitā bhavanti kāyacittapracārāpratyavekṣaṇāt.